  "subject": "Chore: Bump RTD image to ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Bump RTD image to ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13\n\nUpdate .readthedocs.yaml to ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13, replacing\nthe deprecated ubuntu-20.04 image and EOL Python 3.8.\n\nThe docs/tox.ini basepython values were already updated to 3.13 by\nthe earlier mermaid migration change, so this commit only touches\nthe read-the-docs build configuration.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Ibf1579ed542bf47d8199438cda1af84a1228ad00\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
